---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Mo Shaban" description="Learn more about Mo Shaban, software engineer and tech blogger.">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <div class="terminal-controls">
          <span class="control close"></span>
          <span class="control minimize"></span>
          <span class="control maximize"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-title">about_mo.sh</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="terminal-content">
        <div class="command-line">
          <span class="prompt">$</span>
          <span class="command">cat README.md</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="file-content">
          <h1 class="markdown-h1">About Mo Shaban</h1>
          
          <div class="intro-section">
            <div class="code-block">
              <div class="code-header">
                <span class="filename">developer.json</span>
                <span class="language">JSON</span>
              </div>
              <pre is:raw><code>{
  <span class="json-key">"name"</span>: <span class="json-string">"Mo Shaban"</span>,
  <span class="json-key">"role"</span>: <span class="json-string">"Software Engineer"</span>,
  <span class="json-key">"location"</span>: <span class="json-string">"Berlin üá©üá™</span>,
  <span class="json-key">"passion"</span>: <span class="json-string">"Building elegant solutions"</span>,
  <span class="json-key">"languages"</span>: [
    <span class="json-string">"JavaScript"</span>,
    <span class="json-string">"TypeScript"</span>,
    <span class="json-string">"Python"</span>,
  ],
  <span class="json-key">"currentFocus"</span>: <span class="json-string">"Full-stack development"</span>,
  <span class="json-key">"status"</span>: <span class="json-string">"Always learning üìö"</span>
}</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>

          <section class="section">
            <h2 class="markdown-h2">What I Do</h2>
            <div class="content-block">
              <p>
                I specialize in full-stack development and mobile app development, with extensive experience 
                in modern web technologies, React Native, cloud platforms, and software architecture. 
                I enjoy working on projects that make a positive impact and help people solve real-world problems.
              </p>
              
              <div class="tech-stack">
                <div class="stack-category">
                  <h3>Frontend</h3>
                  <div class="tech-tags">
                    <span class="tech-tag react">React ‚öõÔ∏è</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag vue">Remix üíö</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag astro">Astro üöÄ</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag next">Next.js ‚ñ≤</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag postgres">Anything with Cursor</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stack-category">
                  <h3>Mobile</h3>
                  <div class="tech-tags">
                    <span class="tech-tag react-native">React Native üì±</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag expo">Expo üîß</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag postgres">Anything with Cursor</span>
                  </div>
                </div> 
                
                <div class="stack-category">
                  <h3>Backend</h3>
                  <div class="tech-tags">
                    <span class="tech-tag node">Node.js üü¢</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag python">Python üêç</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag postgres">PostgreSQL üêò</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag postgres">Anything with Cursor</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="section">
            <h2 class="markdown-h2">Why I Write</h2>
            <div class="content-block">
              <blockquote class="dev-quote">
                <div class="quote-content">
                  <p>
                    This blog is my way of sharing what I learn, documenting my journey, and hopefully 
                    helping other developers along the way. I believe in the power of knowledge sharing 
                    and the importance of giving back to the community that has taught me so much.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="quote-author">
                  <span class="quote-dash">--</span>
                  <span class="author-name">Mo Shaban</span>
                </div>
              </blockquote>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="section">
            <h2 class="markdown-h2">Get In Touch</h2>
            <div class="content-block">
              <p>
                I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers, discussing new ideas, 
                or collaborating on interesting projects. Feel free to reach out!
              </p>
              
              <div class="contact-methods">
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <span class="contact-icon">üìß</span>
                  <code>echo "hello@moshaban.dev"</code>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <span class="contact-icon">üêô</span>
                  <code>git clone github.com/moshaban</code>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <span class="contact-icon">üê¶</span>
                  <code>curl -X GET twitter.com/moshaban</code>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
        
        <div class="command-line">
          <span class="prompt">$</span>
          <span class="cursor">_</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .terminal-header {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    padding: var(--spacing-sm) var(--spacing-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .terminal-controls {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .control {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .control.close {
    background: var(--accent-error);
  }

  .control.minimize {
    background: var(--accent-warning);
  }

  .control.maximize {
    background: var(--accent-success);
  }

  .control:hover {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px currentColor;
  }

  .terminal-title {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .terminal-content {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .command-line {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .command-line:last-child {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .prompt {
    color: var(--accent-success);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-right: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .command {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .cursor {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    animation: blink 1s infinite;
  }

  .file-content {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .markdown-h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    position: relative;
  }

  .markdown-h1::before {
    content: '# ';
    color: var(--syntax-keyword);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .markdown-h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--syntax-function);
    margin: var(--spacing-2xl) 0 var(--spacing-lg) 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .markdown-h2::before {
    content: '## ';
    color: var(--syntax-keyword);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .intro-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .code-block {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  .code-header {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    padding: var(--spacing-sm) var(--spacing-md);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
  }

  .filename {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .language {
    color: var(--syntax-comment);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
  }

  .code-block pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .code-block code {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  /* JSON syntax highlighting */
  .json-key {
    color: var(--syntax-property);
  }

  .json-string {
    color: var(--syntax-string);
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .content-block {
    margin-left: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .content-block p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .tech-stack {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    margin: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
  }

  .stack-category h3 {
    color: var(--syntax-function);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .tech-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .tech-tag {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    padding: var(--spacing-sm) var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .tech-tag:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .tech-tag.react:hover { border-color: #61dafb; }
  .tech-tag.vue:hover { border-color: #4fc08d; }
  .tech-tag.astro:hover { border-color: #ff5d01; }
  .tech-tag.next:hover { border-color: #000; }
  .tech-tag.node:hover { border-color: #339933; }
  .tech-tag.python:hover { border-color: #3776ab; }
  .tech-tag.go:hover { border-color: #00add8; }
  .tech-tag.postgres:hover { border-color: #336791; }
  .tech-tag.react-native:hover { border-color: #61dafb; }
  .tech-tag.expo:hover { border-color: #000020; }

  .dev-quote {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 0;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .dev-quote::before {
    content: '"""';
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--spacing-sm);
    left: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .quote-content p {
    margin-left: var(--spacing-lg);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .quote-author {
    text-align: right;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .quote-dash {
    color: var(--syntax-comment);
  }

  .author-name {
    color: var(--syntax-function);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .contact-methods {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  .contact-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .contact-item:hover {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .contact-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .contact-item code {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--syntax-string);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .terminal-content {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    }
    
    .markdown-h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .markdown-h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .content-block {
      margin-left: 0;
    }
    
    .tech-stack {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }
    
    .code-block pre {
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .quote-content p {
      margin-left: var(--spacing-md);
    }
  }
</style>